 1628841117, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269332, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": 2269323, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: dz是很温柔的人呢", "timestamp": 1628841214, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269343, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": 2269323, "tag": null, "text": "总结：相信自己，这样做没错。如果真的想要起到一些作用的话，去读一读危机干预的书，看一看案例，保持耐心不要心急。大概掌握一个原则就是：最开始要做到不问、少说、多听，后面可以在不打断对方的基础上边听边说进行交流，再进一步了可以试探性地旁敲侧击，但不可直接问。", "timestamp": 1628841362, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269344, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": 2269255, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 娱乐运动中", "timestamp": 1628841372, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269361, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我就没收到dz的心理援助，我也知道dz是谁", "timestamp": 1628841507, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269403, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": 2269361, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 你向我求助过吗", "timestamp": 1628841759, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269429, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": 2269403, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 没有，看你的描述以为是主动援助", "timestamp": 1628842039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269448, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": 2269429, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是吧。不过对于知道怎么自我援助，以及知道怎么寻求专业的心理援助的朋友，我可能这方面不会那么热心。我一般伸出援手的，是那种我觉得可能对方可能也不知道怎么办的？", "timestamp": 1628842174, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269454, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 436873, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "“以及”改成“或者”", "timestamp": 1628842195, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2269456, "deleted": false, "image